snippet.title: Community Inc Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/631540/Community_Inc/

As a new Manager, build a happy community and trade with other races... for profit. Yes, that's right, we need their happiness so we can power up our portals. The Lings, your workers, will obey you and help you with your village. But beware, they can cause a lot of problems too.

Join our discord - https://discord.gg/gnjFpzC
